{"tid":2310311,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想揾個負責IT既創業伙伴","createTime":"2020-12-03T07:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T05:37:49.000Z","uid":193102,"like":4,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5554573c1f3969616133da2b5967c5badc277a","tid":2310311,"uid":193102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"我做開測量估價,近一年多自學python,用過往二十年樓市成交數據作分析基礎,自己寫左個覆蓋香港近9成住宅物業既估價系統: <a href=\"http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproinfo.pythonanywhere.com%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=d08c2795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/</a><br />\n仲有個簡單既擴展用途: <a href=\"http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproinfo.pythonanywhere.com%2Fsearch&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=bb704ca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/search</a><br />\n係剛剛過去既中大創業日用左展覽,而家同個創投加速器傾緊.<br />\n<br />\n黎緊會揾公司/freelancer寫個target公司客戶既估價平台.<br />\n想揾個負責IT方面既partner.以backend skill為主,最好都要識d frontend<br />\n更多關於此項目的資料: <a href=\"http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproinfo.pythonanywhere.com%2Fhome&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=6977c5c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/home</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你都有心搞初創並欣賞我既idea,請你tg聯絡我啦.<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kei91134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkei91134&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=3928a9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kei91134</a>"},{"pid":"a8940caa312e4c2c16c19a47151dbcc61b1340d1","tid":2310311,"uid":108321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"似乎估價係你個idea其中一個大既賣點, 想請教你既估價比銀行網上即時估價有咩優點? 因為用家估價多數係想做按揭, 點解唔去銀行到做?"},{"pid":"d74471b0830df13bdbbcf7c5ec1b6eaee700e23e","tid":2310311,"uid":193102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8940caa312e4c2c16c19a47151dbcc61b1340d1","tid":2310311,"uid":108321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"似乎估價係你個idea其中一個大既賣點, 想請教你既估價比銀行網上即時估價有咩優點? 因為用家估價多數係想做按揭, 點解唔去銀行到做?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"銀行D網估從來不是最終估價,銀行真做按揭的時候會揾間測量師行做個較認真既估價.<br />\n所以第一步係做個系統比測量師行用,然後再同佢地合作.<br />\n然後仲有其他更主要既發展.<br />\n有興趣的話,網站中的項目簡介有簡單介紹發展方向(<a href=\"http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/static/doc/Proinfo%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%A3%E8%AA%AAv2_Nov2020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproinfo.pythonanywhere.com%2Fstatic%2Fdoc%2FProinfo%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AA%25AAv2_Nov2020.pdf&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5b8d6452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://proinfo.pythonanywhere.com/static/doc/Proinfo%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E8%A7%A3%E8%AA%AAv2_Nov2020.pdf</a>)"},{"pid":"4bbde0d8c936274f6c8bf5715a7b1feb2cb51559","tid":2310311,"uid":63491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"之前有個tech fd試過類似既idea: <a href=\"https://truehome.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruehome.hk&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=65b77f52\" target=\"_blank\">https://truehome.hk</a>"},{"pid":"4991218c6552d5e41eea7b33b911217840426eea","tid":2310311,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cabd116a325999514729149bc6e4e29f4ae164","tid":2310311,"uid":54721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實你寫得出舊果個<br />\n已經有能力寫埋新果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbf47adb390980fa19eeff1a788f0ce40845940","tid":2310311,"uid":193102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor